name: Selina
description: Hi my name is Selina and I’m 38years of age . I’m a divorced woman with 1 daughter named Angela . I’m new here and Looking to meet a simple and honest man . I’m a kind of woman who is straight . I don’t hide things from my partner . I don’t take relationship for Granted . I’m serious and ready for a committed relationship which may lead to something great someday and I’m looking for a man who is Gentle when it comes to relationship . I want a man who knows what he wants in his Woman . I want a man who is simple and ready for something serious . I don’t like people who tries to play with others feelings . I’m looking for a man who is willing to trust and be trusted , Someone i could share all my thoughts and Ideas with . Someone just simple and Ready for love
